  "description": "Product Description:\n\nEmbrace the refined elegance of this lab-grown emerald ring, crafted with a four-prong setting in premium S925 sterling silver. Known for its hypoallergenic and tarnish-resistant properties, S925 silver ensures durability and comfort for daily wear.\n\nAt the heart of this ring is a 6.6x8.5mm, 1.42-carat oval-cut lab-grown emerald with a vibrant green hue, symbolizing growth and renewal. Flanking the central stone are two pear-cut accent stones, adding a touch of sophistication to the timeless three-stone design. With a total accent stone weight of 0.526 carats and weighing 2.55 grams, this ring is lightweight and comfortable, available in sizes 5 to 7.5 (standard U.S. sizing). Please note that lab-grown colored gemstone rings have an estimated shipping time of 3-15 days.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Emerald Center Stone: A stunning 6.6x8.5mm, 1.42-carat oval-cut emerald, symbolizing renewal and vitality.\n\nElegant Three-Stone Design: Flanked by two pear-cut side stones, totaling 0.526 carats, enhancing the central emerald’s allure.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Hypoallergenic and tarnish-resistant, perfect for long-lasting wear.\n\nLightweight Comfort: Weighs 2.55 grams, available in U.S. ring sizes 5 to 7.5.\n\nShipping: Lab-grown colored gemstones ship within 3-15 days.\n\nPerfect for those seeking a sophisticated yet classic piece, this emerald ring brings timeless elegance to any jewelry collection.",
